data.title: Glasunderlägg Svenska fyrar
data.meta_description: Våra glasunderlägg med några av de mest populära fyrarna längs Sveriges kust är enormt populära. De har dubbelsidigt tryck med olika fyrar på var sida. I ett 6-pack får du alltså 12 stycken fyrar. Dubbelt så mycket fyrar för pengarna!  Båtfolk och campingfolk! Underläggen har en inbyggd anti-halkfunktion vilket gör att glaset står still trots att det gungar.
data.text:
Our coasters featuring some of the most popular lighthouses along the Swedish coast are hugely popular. They have a double-sided print with different lighthouses on each side. So in a 6-pack you get 12 lighthouses. Twice as many lighthouses for the money!

Boaters and campers! The coasters have a built-in anti-slip function that keeps the glass stationary even when it's rocking.

Description

The coasters are available in four different series: West Coast, South Coast, East Coast and the stylish the compass roses.

West Coast series includes: Hållö - Måseskär, Pater Noster - Vinga, Tistlarna - Nidingen, Morups Tånge - Tylön, Kullen - Helsingborg and Malmö Inre - Falsterbo.

South Coast series includes: Kullen - Helsingborg, Malmö Inre - Falsterbo, Smygehuk - Sandhammaren, Hanö - Utklippan, Långe Jan - Långe Erik and Stora Karlsö - Gotska Sandön.

East Coast series includes: Långe Jan - Långe Erik, Stora Karlsö - Gotska Sandön, Landsort - Svenska Högarna, Söderarm - Örskär, Brämön - Bergudden and Rödkallen - Malören.

Do you want to match? Here you will find coaster with lighthouses and wine cork in the shape of a lighthouse.

FACTS

100 % food grade silicone. Free from phthalates and bisphenol A (BPA-free).

-50°C to +230°C

Freezer, oven and microwave safe

Machine washable

Colour: navy blue with double-sided red and white heat-resistant print

Size: 9 cm in diameter

Packaging: 6 pieces

Manufacturer: Pufz

Here you can find all marine gifts.
